{"tid":1326020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣周日集會改遊行 銅鑼灣起步至中環終審法院","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:32:51.000Z","uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec845dfd8f23df25323b758e8e0788acd2f7dde1","tid":1326020,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"民陣昨午與警方開會，建議將原定於下周日舉行的金鐘添美道集會改為遊行，惟當日其他團體發起的行動有變，故民陣仍要與警方商討遊行時間、路線等安排，雙方經商討後，宣佈7月21日發起遊行，由銅鑼灣遊行到中環終審法院外。民陣將於今日下午3時在灣仔警總門外召開記者會，公佈詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1546434/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B9%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1546434%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aueNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=ee89fff5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1546434%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2&h=8a0f8ac4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1546434/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%91%A8%E6%97